{"tid":483581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［金融創新］「裸貸」變身「佳麗貸」　女生愈靚借得愈多　無力還錢賣往夜場","createTime":"2017-11-29T08:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T10:19:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db7909bbb1561de83d1f7adb1a9fb6b7be2f3288","tid":483581,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"去年內地出現「裸貸」不良風氣，即不法分子逼借貸女生以手持自己身分證的裸照作抵押，若欠款不還即把照片放上網，導致部分借貸人不堪受辱自殺。有關問題引起當局關注，惟問題尚未解決，「裸貸」卻已變種為「佳麗貸」，即不法貸款公司專向年輕貌美女子入手，愈漂亮貸款額愈高，待她們無力還錢，即逼令對方到夜場賣淫還債。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地傳媒報道，湖南省長沙市一間名為「融e富」的網絡貸款公司，近日推出「佳麗貸款」，以「顏值高低」來評斷貸款額度，只要是年滿18歲至28歲的女性，僅憑一張身分證即能借款1至10萬元(人民幣，下同)，沒有其他條件，不查看負債紀錄及還款能力，更保證貸款即日到手。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒記者前往「放蛇」，接頭人直言「長得高一點，長得漂亮一點，我們的貸款額度就高一點」，又稱「沒工作也沒關係，漂亮一點就可，利息什麼的以後再談」。記者開口借3萬元，對方即答應，其後談到如借兩萬，需兩個月內還清，每日要還800元，即本金連利息需還近5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n接頭人更揚言如逾期還款後果很嚴重，需由他們安排到KTV或酒店等地方陪酒，即要借貸者賣身抵債。事件經報道後，當局介入調查，現已查處涉及無證經營的融e富。<br />\n<br />\n(東方網、梨視頻)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171129/s00004/1511922910452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171129%2Fs00004%2F1511922910452&d=%2BajzBnAb0PlQEQmw%2Fg88uv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d38f9f58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171129%2Fs00004%2F1511922910452&h=b384292f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171129/s00004/1511922910452</a>"},{"pid":"874a360ae2d2de57305bfe838150574d0222bcb1","tid":483581,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13af17dd19ca2ee519b852f12c475939d7a9e6c3","tid":483581,"uid":29423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"Credit assessment 係睇個body 既NPV in prostitution industry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[9up學術mode]"},{"pid":"0b9ef23e63e16787305ab576e2c8d973601bcf69","tid":483581,"uid":90166,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"中國真係先進過香港好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759a263544bef51076eb8cb5fa6bfdebf1c40ee3","tid":483581,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"處應該雙計，應該驗埋閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2aed3f0eec106247123085be3cbbc2cdf138f55","tid":483581,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc94843458ac184bf83221e3c99a9b8edf4d28d","tid":483581,"uid":56533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"忠告 : 借錢唔撚還, 賣你做雞還債"},{"pid":"883c2e1ccdda1b105c0f34f5b4b6a1c85304e321","tid":483581,"uid":34666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"雷教授試過都話好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46101a08d7b8e15511d8ac2b3bd7050989e360c8","tid":483581,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國真係先進過香港好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個case認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd8c7e56cc7e0428a07c73cf3d3a5fd2004b0a9","tid":483581,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>融e富</del></span><br />\n溶衣褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d59a9b9